author: Trish Turner, Sarah Kolinovsky
title: Small business rescue program runs out of money amid political standoff
description: As thousands of small businesses owners across the country scramble to stay afloat, the loan program rain out money to run out of money Thursday morning.
content:
Thousands of small business owners across the U.S. have been left in the lurch as the popular federal government-backed loan program meant to save them and protect worker paychecks in the pandemic fallout officially ran out of money Thursday morning.
